Interface IModifyElement

public interface IModifyElement

Represents the modify-element child of a configuration-data-delta element.

Since:
4.0.4

getSetAttributes

java.util.List getSetAttributes()
Get the list of ISetAttribute that describe the attribute modifications to be performed on the element specified by the path. The list might be empty but should never be null.

getSetText

Returns:
ISetText or null if no set-text was specified.
